name: Kosas_Home_'Alicia'_72-inch_Sheesham_Wood_Dining_Table
reviews: The table is beautiful...the variation in grain makes it look very expensive. It appears very well made. I might add a coat of poly to make sure that the top doesn't get nicked up

We love our new table! Recommended by Customer Service after another table was out of stock, it is truly the perfect table for our family. It was a little tall compared to what we were used to, but we cut a few inches off the legs with a table saw and it's perfect now. It is dark and heavy but totally unconventional. Cuts a fine figure, bohos up that farmhouse style we have going on. Would highly recommend. (but measure your chairs first!)

This table is beautiful. Easy to put together and solid wood. only regret that I didn't get the 96' with the drop down leaves. But this will seat 8 and the chairs are pricey so more table length is more chairs. Either way, still love it and it's perfect
description:
This Alicia wood dining table is constructed from solid sheesham wood to provide a smooth and stable surface for all your dining needs. A natural finish and clean straight lines give this rectangular dining table its rustic country feel. Surround this table with mismatched chairs for a fun and unique look.
